About Las Ventanas

Charm convenience and quiet in Pleasanton one, two and three bedroom homes plus single story cottages in Prime Pleasanton location. Easy commute, Interstate 680 just 5 minutes away. Call now for your private tour at Las Ventanas, a welcome place to call home.
